video.title: Storage Wars: Collection
video.synopsis: When the contents of unpaid storage units go to auction, a crew of opportunists gather to bid on what could be gold mines ... or rooms full of junk.

episodes.synopsis: Darrell re-emerges after scoring the biggest hit in "Storage Wars" history, and Mark shows up with a custom-made man purse full of money.
episodes.title: Auctioning for Dummies

episodes.synopsis: Barry brings "the King of Kitsch" to view an auction, Darrell learns a lesson about home-field advantage, and Jarrod buys solo -- at a price.
episodes.title: Breathalyze This

episodes.synopsis: The buyers run into "the King of Palmdale," a former ultimate fighter who gets into the ring and spars with Darrell. Jarrod and Brandi meet a nerd.
episodes.title: The Big Boy vs. The Heavyweight

episodes.synopsis: Barry hires psychics who get a "dark" feeling at one auction. But that doesn't spook Jarrod and Brandi, who take a unit that could save their store.
episodes.title: Midnight in the Gardena Good and Evil

episodes.synopsis: Jarrod and Brandi uncover what appears to be an antique wine rack; Dave and Barry test each other's knowledge; and Darrell just wants some gas money.
episodes.title: Trouble the Oil

episodes.synopsis: Darrell takes a stab at Dave's store; Brandi and Jarrod argue over the value of a bizarre find; and Dave makes his strangest discovery ever!
episodes.title: Skullduggery

episodes.synopsis: Dave Hester bids on a unit with a stockpile of antiques. Barry Weiss lands himself a locker previously owned by a man with an antique weapons fetish.
episodes.title: Buyers on the Storm

episodes.synopsis: A mysterious bidder aims to dominate the competition, Darrell vies for a drum set, Jarrod and Brandi face loss, and Dave duels with his new nemesis.
episodes.title: Enemy of the Enemy

episodes.synopsis: Darrell fishes for a locker, Barry spies some antique militaria, Dave can't get in the game, and Jarrod and Brandi take a shine to a jewelry box.
episodes.title: Tanks for the Memories

episodes.synopsis: Jarrod and Brandi's gains fade; Barry becomes an organ donor; Dave shows that sometimes not making a deal makes sense; Darrell relies on a coin toss.
episodes.title: Land of the Loss

episodes.synopsis: "The Mogul" and "The Young Gun" clash, Barry heads to the big top, and Dave bids on one of the biggest lockers in "Storage Wars" history.
episodes.title: Almost the Greatest Show on Earth

episodes.synopsis: Darrell's son advances to the next level of buying -- at Jarrod and Brandi's expense. Barry gambles on a locker that yields more than chicken feed.
episodes.title: Winner Winner Chicken Dinner

episodes.synopsis: Barry loses a battle with a bot, Darrell goes on a run, Dave heads straight to the bank, and Jarrod and Brandi wish they never came to the auction.
episodes.title: The Full Monty-Bello

episodes.synopsis: Too many choices and too much heat make it hard for Jarrod and Brandi, and tensions mount between Dave and Darrell's son Brandon.
episodes.title: The Yup Stops Here

episodes.synopsis: Jeff Jarred resurfaces, which upsets the Dotsons. Barry figures a couple of things out, and Jarrod and Brandi gamble -- with electrifying results.
episodes.title: The Young and the Reckless
